name: The CMS Company Search page supports searching for company details.
fullName: tests/features/optionMenu.feature#The CMS Company Search page supports searching for company details.

steps.name: Given I am logged into the CMS application
When I click the "DataManagementMenu" on the "homePage" Page
And I click the "CompanyManagementMenu" on the "homePage" Page
And I click the "CompaniesMenu" on the "homePage" Page
Then I verify that the "Companies" page is displayed
And I click the option menu
Then I verified Option menu popup
And I log out from the CMS application
